Sir, before you do that,

21:07.249 --> 21:08.933
maybe you'd like to try
another puzzle?

21:09.084 --> 21:10.159
This one's a little harder.

21:10.252 --> 21:12.252
It's a hundred pieces, and, uh,

21:12.346 --> 21:14.013
two of the unicorns
look pretty similar.

21:14.165 --> 21:16.256
Clear my calendar!
Lock the door!

